{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How did you get here?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After befriending your first <strong>Ghost</strong> in the abandoned Arcade Hall, he asks you to retrieve any Ghosts that are trapped inside the Arcade Games!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What do you do now?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In order to retrieve the first 100 pieces, you must dive into the world of the Arcade Game Drama Llama and find every last fragment to free every soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And if you feel up to it, you can dive into 2 distinct Arcade Game experiences and retrieve the last 200 Ghosts trapped in them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888450/extras/hiddensquaregif.gif?t=1737843996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What then?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can compete against the whole world in global leaderboards by finding the 100 Ghosts exceedingly quicker!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">And after that?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can create your own levels or download user-created ones, including their own leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(Level Editor DLC sold separately for 0.99$. I would like to keep the entire game free, but I sadly have to make back thhe 100$ Steam Fee and get funny stuff like tax advisers that keep me out of jail.)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Why would you do all that just to click Ghosts?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Because it is just so much fun! Seriously. It is also cozy and relaxing. But most of all, every pop you hear from finding a Ghost releases a bit more dopamine.<br><br><br>Thank you for reading this and have a great day! :)</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888450/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737843996","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888450/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1737843996","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888450/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737843996","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888450/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737843996","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Leaderboards","id":25},{"description":"Includes level editor","id":17}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">How did you get here?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After befriending your first <strong>Ghost</strong> in the abandoned Arcade Hall, he asks you to retrieve any Ghosts that are trapped inside the Arcade Games!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What do you do now?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In order to retrieve the first 100 pieces, you must dive into the world of the Arcade Game Drama Llama and find every last fragment to free every soul.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">And if you feel up to it, you can dive into 2 distinct Arcade Game experiences and retrieve the last 200 Ghosts trapped in them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2888450/extras/hiddensquaregif.gif?t=1737843996\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What then?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can compete against the whole world in global leaderboards by finding the 100 Ghosts exceedingly quicker!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">And after that?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can create your own levels or download user-created ones, including their own leaderboards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">(Level Editor DLC sold separately for 0.99$. I would like to keep the entire game free, but I sadly have to make back thhe 100$ Steam Fee and get funny stuff like tax advisers that keep me out of jail.)</p><p class=\"